      "author": {
        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-08-04T18:14:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Seems like this should be shared code too. CPU-specific, but not Linux-specific.\n\nIt wouldn’t be totally out of place in the new cpuid file, even though it’s not cpuid instruction-based.",
      "revId": "32c4e043d8d526c7409ca5d147fbe6732a38b604",
